---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About" description="About refracted.space — space engineering, Zurich, identity.">
  <section class="container about fade-up">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body content-width">
      <p>
        I'm a (future) space engineer based in Zürich. This is where I write about
        orbital mechanics, satellite systems, life in Switzerland, and the
        space between languages and identities.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>refracted.space</strong> is named for what happens when light
        passes through a medium and bends - changes direction without changing
        nature. That feels like a useful metaphor for living between cultures,
        disciplines, and ways of seeing.
      </p>

      <h2>Colophon</h2>

      <p>
        This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>,
        styled with plain CSS, set in
        <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Outfit">Outfit</a>,
        <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Space+Grotesk">Space Grotesk</a>, and
        <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/lp/mono/">JetBrains Mono</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        The design follows editorial principles: bold typography,
        strong hierarchy, monochrome palette, and nothing that doesn't earn
        its place.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>

      <p>
        You can reach me by email at
        <a href="mailto:asametoglu@ethz.ch">asametoglu@ethz.ch</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-header {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0 var(--space-12);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .about-body {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-body a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .about-body ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header {
      padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-8);
    }
  }
</style>
